this nice guide &lt;a href="http://www.maketecheasier.com/install-encfs-mac/"&gt;http://www.maketecheasier.com/install-encfs-mac/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">admin</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2013 21:17:00 +0000</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:www.andreagrandi.it,2013-11-08:/2013/11/08/how-to-fix-encfs-installation-on-osx-10-9-mavericks-and-brew/</guid><category>HowTo, OSX, Sicurezza</category><category>cloud</category><category>encfs</category><category>encryption</category><category>fuse4x</category><category>OSX</category><category>security</category></item></channel></rss>